> This is just a simple rest api made using node.js express and mongodb along with mongoose

TOOLS used: 

- Insomnia
- mongoDB Compass

Clone this repo
Make sure you install all the dependencies
Make sure you have mongoDB service running
 `npm run start` to start the proj

I have added a localhost url along with a port for now
.env.example is just an example to show how a .env file will look like (don't alter)

> http://localhost:${PORT}/check to check the json data (dummy data). 

> Will be adding more features (still incomplete)

[idea]: derived from anime-chan api 
